name: KISS WOMEN'S GUNMETAL HOODY
description: The "kiss" design is one of our favorite designs. The front of the hoody has a very detail design of lips. Underneath the lips has a phrase that says "embrasser mon A**" which means "kiss my a**" in French. For ultimate comfort the design is printed on 60% Cotton 40% Polyester premium hoody. name: SAMO CHARCOAL CREWNECK
description: The SAMO design pays homage to Jean-Michel Basquiat. SAMO which stands for "same old shit" was Jean-Michel Basquiat's graffiti tag name. The design has a very artsy feel because of the contour line drawing of the letters and crown which Basquiat often had in his paintings. For ultimate comfort the design is printed on 90% cotton 10% polyester premium sweatshirt. The garment fits true to size.

name: POOR & DANGEROUS ASH CREWNECK
description: The Poor & Dangerous design is inspired by Hip-Hop artist Big L's first studio album entitled, "Lifestyles ov da Poor & Dangerous". The title of the design is very powerful because anyone from the inner city or living in poverty can relate to it and understand the struggle. The graphic on the design has a middle eastern child holding an AK-47. The graphic is bold with vibrant color schemes that draws the consumer in. For ultimate comfort the design is printed on 10 oz 90% cotton 10% polyester. The garment fits true to size.
